HEADWORD: Sacristy
<hw>Sac"ris*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Sacristies</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[F. <ets>sacristie</ets>,
